data.title: UPL: Yarmolenko returns and scores as Dynamo beat Vorskla
data.meta_description: UPL: Yarmolenko returns and scores as Dynamo beat Vorskla. The biggest match of the 22nd round between Vorskla and Dynamo was overshadowed by a long air raid warning
data.text:
The biggest match of the 22nd round between Vorskla and Dynamo was overshadowed by a long air raid warning, but this did not stop the teams from delighting the fans with a large number of goals.

This was also the first game in six month for Andriy Yarmolenko, who recently recovered from his injury.

2023-24, Ukraine - Premier League
